show.description: A small doll harbors a terrifying spirit, thirsty for blood! This story unfolds a series of horror and dread that will keep you awake all night. When a mother buys an old doll for her son, she has no idea that this doll is about to bring the shadow of death into their home. A thrilling journey filled with spirits, ghosts, and witches—watch it only in *Paapi Gudiya*.
